items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

What happens when you take two or more amazing breweries, throw them into the tank and let them ferment together? An amazing collaboration beer, thats what! Cheers to working together to create the perfect flavor. That's 25 different beers that have been brewed as a collaboration. Try 5 more for Level 6!

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 370 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 75!

What happens when you take two or more amazing breweries, throw them into the tank and let them ferment together? An amazing collaboration beer, thats what! Cheers to working together to create the perfect flavor. That's 45 different beers that have been brewed as a collaboration. Try 5 more for Level 10!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 195 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 40! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
